    "canonical": "Bolts from this Corpus bow deliver a one-two punch of an icy pulse, followed by a conventional explosion. Excess ammo picked up for other weapons will be converted into charges for the Lenz. \r\n\r\nWarning: Safety-protocols do not exist on this prototype.",
